                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2001-07-05</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This book is a very good general view of freud's ideas, theories, and views. I would recommend it if you are just stating out. It has clear language too. However it is not terribly indepth so be forewarned that it may not meet all needs. It is a good general resource though.</span>
                  
              
